{"tid":1895945,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"作家君比逝世 曾著多部受歡迎青少年小說","createTime":"2020-02-24T23:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T16:07:52.000Z","uid":133680,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a726e0e8d32ebe20bafe16602d13d5b4f766fde2","tid":1895945,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T23:41:12.000Z","msg":"君比老師於前晚(2月23日)與世長辭。她曾榮獲香港《中學生好書龍虎榜》的最受歡迎作家。網民指小時候常常去圖書館借《叛逆歲月》、《四個10A的少年》、《反斗紅娘: Miss絮語》看，是好很多九十後的童年回憶，甚至是很多小學生和初中生的啟蒙讀物！<br />\n<br />\n君比原名馮忻忻，是香港作家，原籍廣東南海，畢業於德蘭中學。「君比」這個筆名來自她的第一部小說《君比》，而這個名字亦同時是她的英文名譯音。<br />\n<br />\n她擅長於描寫青春期的少男少女在心態和情感上的轉變，描寫得特別細緻，而且有不少都是真人真事改編，一定程度反映社會現實。現時君比全職寫作，並經常到全香港各中、小學推廣閱讀及寫作。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.modia.com.hk/2020/02/24/164020/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%9B%E6%AF%94%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E9%81%BA%E4%B9%9D%E5%8D%81%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E3%80%8A%E5%8F%9B%E9%80%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.modia.com.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F24%2F164020%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%2590%259B%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E7%2597%2585%25E9%2580%259D-%25E9%2581%25BA%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25BE%258C%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2586%25B6%25E3%2580%258A%25E5%258F%259B%25E9%2580%2586%2F&d=MxNsT%2FmsUjaXWzHBtsAqwdXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=7ce9fa48\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.modia.com.hk/2020/02/24/164020/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BD%9C%E5%AE%B6%E5%90%9B%E6%AF%94%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E7%97%85%E9%80%9D-%E9%81%BA%E4%B9%9D%E5%8D%81%E5%BE%8C%E7%AB%A5%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E3%80%8A%E5%8F%9B%E9%80%86/</a>"},{"pid":"9690a63f9dd548e86a9791981843ea23d3234afe","tid":1895945,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-25T00:00:47.000Z","msg":"rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d7717229442067a8f4617240429fb422ed3ef3a","tid":1895945,"uid":121504,"lik